line_1: Het reeking frae spit and frae pat:
line_2: Weel plenished wi' raisins and fat,

line_1: Gives one a squeeze, another a kind pat;
line_2: She smiles on this man, tips the wink on that,

line_1: WHO presses on my knee this kindly pat,
line_2: Comest thou to woo my notice, little Matt?

line_1: Or drive it devious with a dex'trous pat,
line_2: To pitch the ball into the grounded hat,

line_1: Till something held within the pat,
line_2: An' ay the win't, an' ay the swat,

line_1: Your Worship's words come in so pat,
line_2: I were an ass to think of that —
